text: Alexeyevka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Samosdelsky Selsoviet, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 201 as of 2010. There are three streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km south-west from Kamyzyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kamyzyaksky District
title: Alexeyevka, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast
